title: Danger Zones - Choose Your Own Super Adventure #2.pdf
description:
Here is the 2nd Choose Your Own Super Adventure.  Unfortunately, this is the last Super Adventure to ever be published... in December 1987.  Because this is a "Super Adventure", it has about 40 more pages than a typical CYOA book.

Details on back:
After waiting for years, you've finally been invited to join the daring Society of Adventurers.  And as a new member, you must choose to embark upon one of three dangerous missions.  You can head to the Takia Makan Desert to hunt for a lost caravan.  You can search for priceless documents in the Himalayas.  Or you can track down two Americans who have vanished without a trace in the Hong Kong underworld!

Enjoy
